/*
BACKGROUND

The default background is solid white, 
to change it, we should treat it like any other transformation

The background has a default transformation of [ h 0 sat 0 b 1 a 1 ]
This means it's normally opaque white.

*/

startshape spotlight


// Let's change the brightness from 1 to 0
// to make the background black:
CF::Background = [ b -1 ]

shape spotlight
{
  CIRCLE [ b 1 sat 1 h 50 s 1 0.5 ]
  spotlight [ y .04 s 0.98 h -2 a -0.1 ] // light cone
}